  "detailed_description": "Fight off endless enemy waves and make it to the exit to progress to the next level. If you die...you start all over again<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Procedurally generated levels, there are an endless amount of them.<br></li><li> Simple keyboard and mouse controls.<br></li><li> Mousewheel Zooming</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><br>Version 2<br><br><strong>Endless Heck</strong><br><br>Fight off endless enemy waves and make it to the exit to progress to the next level. If you die...you start all over again.<br><br>Version 1<br><br><strong>Race Mode</strong><br><br>Race Mode is a battle to get to the exit as fast as you can against the AI.<br><br><strong>Slingshot Mode</strong><br><br>Slingshot your way to the exit as fast as you can, by dragging your mouse to aim and fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.poster.avif?t=1671778134\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.webm?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.mp4?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explode Mode</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.poster.avif?t=1671778134\" width=200 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.webm?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.mp4?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Avoid the walls and get to the exit as fast as you can.<br><br><strong>Sprint Mode</strong><br><br>In this mode you can hit the walls, use it to practice a run before entering Explode Mode or Rogue Mode<br><br><strong>Rogue Mode</strong><br><br>The ultimate challenge! Hit the wall, you die and go all the way back to level 1.<br><br><strong>Countdown Mode</strong><br><br>You have 10 seconds to get the exit. Don't hit the walls!",
  "about_the_game": "Fight off endless enemy waves and make it to the exit to progress to the next level. If you die...you start all over again<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Procedurally generated levels, there are an endless amount of them.<br></li><li> Simple keyboard and mouse controls.<br></li><li> Mousewheel Zooming</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><br>Version 2<br><br><strong>Endless Heck</strong><br><br>Fight off endless enemy waves and make it to the exit to progress to the next level. If you die...you start all over again.<br><br>Version 1<br><br><strong>Race Mode</strong><br><br>Race Mode is a battle to get to the exit as fast as you can against the AI.<br><br><strong>Slingshot Mode</strong><br><br>Slingshot your way to the exit as fast as you can, by dragging your mouse to aim and fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.poster.avif?t=1671778134\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.webm?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/583a311bab1b48bb6e0304004c849dad.mp4?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explode Mode</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.poster.avif?t=1671778134\" width=200 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.webm?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623060/extras/e7c48313093c04d653bf84ee420dd938.mp4?t=1671778134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Avoid the walls and get to the exit as fast as you can.<br><br><strong>Sprint Mode</strong><br><br>In this mode you can hit the walls, use it to practice a run before entering Explode Mode or Rogue Mode<br><br><strong>Rogue Mode</strong><br><br>The ultimate challenge! Hit the wall, you die and go all the way back to level 1.<br><br><strong>Countdown Mode</strong><br><br>You have 10 seconds to get the exit. Don't hit the walls!",
